    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Parotoplana spathifera sp. n. A, Sclerotized apparatus. Scale = 30 µm. B, Reconstruction of the genital organs from sagittal sections. Scale = 60 µm. Abbreviations are the same as Fig 1." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/177650/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.177654>
    dc:description "FIGURE 6. Parotoplana pythagorae sp. n. A, Sagittal section (paratype). Scale = 50 µm. B, Sclerotized apparatus (holotype). Scale = 30 µm. C, Sagittal section of the paratype. Scale = 50 µm. Parotoplana spathifera sp. n. D, Sclerotized apparatus (holotype). Scale = 30 µm. E, Sagittal section (paratype). Scale = 30 µm. Abbreviations are the same as Fig 1." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/177654/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

